'******************************************************************************
'******************************************************************************

	Forked by Jet Fontanilla 2013/11/08
	
	Bug fixes:
	- URL encodes the token secret before creating the OAuth signtaure
	
	New features:	
	
	objOauth.TokenSecret = "d982fcc10234"
	- sets a custom token secret for your OAuth request
	
	objOauth.Payload = "{'user_id':1}"
	- sets the payload you want to send
	
	objOauth.ContentType = "application/json"
	- sets the content type of the OAuth request. default is application/x-www-form-urlencoded
